# integer-multiple-trailing-spaces

## Input

```
a 42   
b -7   

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..16
  ENTRY@0..8
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    INTEGER@2..4
      NUMERAL@2..4 "42"
    SPACE@4..7 "   "
    NEWLINE@7..8 "\n"
  ENTRY@8..16
    WORD_KEY@8..9
      WORD@8..9 "b"
    SPACE@9..10 " "
    INTEGER@10..12
      MINUS@10..11 "-"
      NUMERAL@11..12 "7"
    SPACE@12..15 "   "
    NEWLINE@15..16 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "a",
            },
            value: Integer {
                sign: none,
                numeral: NUMERAL@2..4 "42",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@8..9 "b",
            },
            value: Integer {
                sign: MINUS@10..11 "-",
                numeral: NUMERAL@11..12 "7",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

